Class LongestCommonSubsequence

  • java.lang.Object
    • LongestCommonSubsequence

  • public class LongestCommonSubsequence
extends java.lang.Object
    LongestCommonSubsequence is a program that will determine the longest string that is a subsequence of two input strings. This program applies a brute force solution technique.
